}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "HU-834 V1.0" and "MADE IN TAIWAN" is silkscreened on the unit populating this entry. <!-- well, partially. haphazard opening of the case meant the hub lost a SMT capacitor and resistor (RIP C22 [pin 25, Vcc] and R9) and gained a large gash on the board. aside from now registering w/ a 0000:0000 USB ID, it ''seems'' to be working (WOO) --> :The radial capacitors on the board are all '''Canicon''' branded. :The USB connectors are all from '''ACON''' (or at least, they all bear their name). :It is also using a '''Micrel''' MIC29302BT High-Current LDO Regulator and a '''Texas Instruments''' TPS2044 USB power switch.
